Class AbstractCurrencyExchanger

java.lang.Object

All Implemented Interfaces:
CurrencyExchanger
public abstract class AbstractCurrencyExchanger
extends Object
implements CurrencyExchanger

Base class for currency exchangers. Provides the functionality for processing exchanges. Subclasses must provide functionality for determining currency exchange rates.
